parsed.explanation: 1. Added an <NR> tag to properly structure the item number. 2. Removed garbage characters ('\u221a\u2020') which appeared to be a transcription error. 3. Added a <NOTE> tag to group the descriptive text about the first book, preserving the nested <FORMAT> tag. 4. Added <NOTE> tags to encapsulate other untagged text fragments describing the transaction. 5. Corrected the malformed structure by adding a missing closing </BIBL> tag. 6.
